research_municipality_step.notes: The elected officials for Marlin, Texas, include the Mayor and six Council Members. Susan R. Byrd serves as Mayor. Joe Mark Taylor is the Mayor Pro-Tem and Council Member for Precinct 6. Other Council Members are William Roe (Precinct 1), Morris Watson Jr. (Precinct 2), Terence W. McDavid (Precinct 3), and Cecil Sparks (Precinct 5). Michael Milnes is also listed as a Council Member. Scottie Henderson, previously listed as Council Member for Precinct 4, had a term expiring in May 2024, and is not included in this current list.
